tart meeting people in the community. They have no cash prize and are on a =
rolling timeline.</p>
<h2>How do I create and manage a team?</h2>
<p>When you accept the competition rules, a team will be created for you. Y=
ou can invite others to your team, accept a merger with another team, and u=
